verses.verse: Praise <S%H1984><s%> ye <S%H3050>Jehovah<s%>. <S%H1984>Praise<s%>, O ye <S%H5650>servants<s%> of <S%H3050>Jehovah<s%>, <S%H1984>Praise<s%> the <S%H8034>name<s%> of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>.
Blessed <S%H1288><s%> be the <S%H8034>name<s%> of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> From this time <S%H6258>forth<s%> and <S%H5704>for<s%> <S%H5769>evermore<s%>.
From the <S%H4217>rising<s%> of the <S%H8121>sun<s%> unto the going <S%H3996>down<s%> of the same <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>'s <S%H8034>name<s%> is to be <S%H1984>praised<s%>.
Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> is <S%H7311>high<s%> <S%H7311>above<s%> all <S%H1471>nations<s%>, And his <S%H3519>glory<s%> <S%H7311>above<s%> the <S%H8064>heavens<s%>.
Who is like unto <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> our <S%H430>God<s%>, That hath his <S%H3427>seat<s%> on <S%H1361>high<s%>,
That <S%H8213>humbleth<s%> himself to <S%H7200>behold<s%> The things that are in <S%H8064>heaven<s%> and in the <S%H776>earth<s%>?
He raiseth <S%H6965>up<s%> the <S%H1800>poor<s%> out of the <S%H6083>dust<s%>, And <S%H7311>lifteth<s%> up the <S%H34>needy<s%> from the <S%H830>dunghill<s%>;
That he may <S%H3427>set<s%> him with <S%H5081>princes<s%>, Even with the <S%H5081>princes<s%> of his <S%H5971>people<s%>.

He maketh the barren <S%H6135>woman<s%> to <S%H3427>keep<s%> <S%H1004>house<s%>, And to be a <S%H8056>joyful<s%> <S%H517>mother<s%> of <S%H1121>children<s%>. <S%H1984>Praise<s%> ye <S%H3050>Jehovah<s%>.
